data.description: With a spectacular 180-degree views of the water and the 7th, 8th, and 9th holes of English Turn's fabulous golf course, this home's location is the envy of the neighborhood.   This home has been metriculously maintained; within the past two-three years, the home's HVAC systems, water heaters, and kitchen appliances have been replaced and in the past year, the windows in the home have also been replaced.  Home was remodeled to enhance the foyer and entry from the foyer to the living room.  Crown molding exists throughout the home with built-in cabinetry several rooms of the home as well as wainscotting in the foyer and dining room.  The second floor boasts tray ceiings in both the media and principal bedroom.  A second-level balcony provides great views.  The home has a three-car garage and a Tesla electric plug in.  What more could you ask for?  Location!  This home is located in New Orleans premier gated golf course community of English Turn with country club, fitness center, tennis courts, swimming pool, 26 acres of parks and fitness trails and 24-7 security.  X Flood zone to boost.  It truely is a great place to call home!
